snippet.title: VTOL VR - EF-24G Mischief DLC: Electronic Warfare Fighter Trailer
snippet.description:
The EF-24G Mischief DLC is out now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2531290/VTOL_VR_EF24_Mischief__Electronic_Warfare/

The EF-24G "Mischief" is a two-seat, twin-engine, variable-sweep fighter aircraft which has been adapted and equipped to play a major role in electronic warfare (EW). Specialized sensors and advanced multi-mode ECM pods give it the capability to find, target, and wreak havoc on all kinds of enemy transmissions. 

Game: VTOL VR
